column5: When my computer took a nose dive. I lost all my links to muskie lure whole Sellers.  If it's alright, can some one post some places for me.
....No favours allowed! Only cause it's you.
NO!!!  You have enough lures honey  Joey
Spiel, If I wasn't so tired from shoveling snow. I would have something to say about that.
....All those fancy toys you have and yet you still shovel?
Oh, I forgot to mention, There for you Hon
TJ can we really help out Paul and block Joey from this thread  ( if you can't please change my post  )
Paul,I can't believe Joey said you couldn't have any more. All along I thought she was the perfect wife.

At least Joey goes fishing.  My wife knows there's absolutely nothing on a fishing related website that I would ever buy for her. I just tell her I'm buying something and that's it. If she squawks, I remind her about the small fortune she spends on coffee.
